title: BILLABONG: A BIKINI KINDA LIFE
description:
A string around her waist, a strap over her shoulder. Her bikini is her second skin. Where she goes, it goes. Sheʼs a wanderer, an explorer, a sun chaser, a wave racer. A thrill seeker, a summer dreamer, a local babe with a worldly spirit. Red sand, white sand, black sand, pink. Deep blue, cobalt, turquoise, green; colours
that provide the backdrop to her life. Summer is in her blood. She belongs to the salt and the salt belongs to her.
She lives #abikinikindalife. And she always wears Billabong.
